text: "Air Force Ones'" is a 2002 pop-rap song by American rapper Nelly. The song features the hip hop group St. Lunatics. It was the fourth single from his second album Nellyville. The song was released on November 7, 2002. The song reached number 3 on the U.S. Billboard Hot 100, number 1 on the U.S. Billboard Hot R&B;/Hip-Hop Singles & Tracks and number 1 on the U.S. Billboard Hot Rap Tracks charts.
